1068. Product Sales Analysis I:

#1.Domain context & #2.PROBLEM STATEMENT:

BIGC 

IT HAS MULTIPLE Product

ONE OF THE PRODUCTS IS MOBILE

IN MOBILES ,THEY HAVE VARITIES OF BRAND

#NOKIA,APPLE,SAMSUNG - THESE PRODUCT INFORMATION CAPTURE IN PRODUCT TABLE

#THEY SOLD ABOVE BRAND MOBILES IN THE SHOW ROOM -SALES TRASCATION INFORMATION CAPTURED 
IN Sales table
LIKE SALE ID,PRODUCTID,YEAR,QUANTITY,PRICE



#3.Approach

PRIMARY TABLE: SALES TABLE
SECONDARY TABLE:PRODUCT TABLE


CLUES:
JOIN-PRODUCTNAME,YEAR,PRICE (PRODUCT NAME PRODUCT TABLE WHERE AS YEAR AND PRICE INFOR SALES TABLE)
LEFT JOIN-EACH SALES ID (SO ALL SALES DATA FROM LEFT TABLE)

















 

